"{\"uid\": \"sakshipost.com-news-olympics-samantha-tapsee-back-vinesh-phogat-after-disqualification-321599\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The entire nation was heartbroken to hear that Vinesh Phogat had been disqualified from the Paris Olympics 2024 due to being 100 grams overweight.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 47, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The whole country, along with celebrities, came in support and comforted Vinesh Phogat for missing the chance to bag a gold medal.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was the first woman to get into finals in wrestling but was disqualified before finals for a weight of 100 grams over 50 kgs.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the announcement, the excitement of seeing India in the finals went in vain.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 458, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999940892586954, \"rank\": 5.909264650307265e-06, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prime Minister Narendra Modi also came out in support of Tollywood and Bollywood celebrities.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telugu_cinema\", \"score\": 0.9999999956169177, \"rank\": 4.383188317699324e-09, \"text\": \"Tollywood\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telugu_cinema\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telugu_cinema\"}, {\"begin\": 563, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\", \"score\": 0.9999999996362021, \"rank\": 2.771181945474301e-10, \"text\": \"Bollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bollywood celebrities like Farah Akhtar, Tapsee Pannu, Sonakshi Sinha, and others shared their support on social media.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\", \"score\": 0.9727135386382787, \"rank\": 0.017792672343704567, \"text\": \"Farah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tapsee Pannu said she was heartbroken by the news and had gone beyond the gold medal.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sonakshi stated, \\\"I do not even know how to console myself at a time like this.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is hard to imagine the pain you are going through right now.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All I can say is that you will always be a champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vicky Kaushal expressed his thoughts and supported Vinesh, saying, \\\"You are a winner beyond medals.\\\"\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Kaushal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vicky Kaushal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Kaushal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Kaushal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tollywood star Samantha took her social media handle to help the player, saying, \\\"Sometimes, people who fight face the most challenging obstacles.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1108, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samantha_Ruth_Prabhu\", \"score\": 0.9999999999040483, \"rank\": 9.582955581346208e-11, \"text\": \"Samantha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samantha_Ruth_Prabhu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samantha_Ruth_Prabhu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember you are not alone, and come back stronger.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's truly admirable to persevere through so many difficulties with your unique ability.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read More:  News|Politics|Entertainment|Lifestyle|Sports|Photos|Videos|Tech|Live TV|e-Paper|Education|Sakshi|Y.S.R|About Us|Contact Us|Privacy Policy|Media Kit|SakshiTV Complaint Redressal  \\u00a9 Copyright Sakshi Post 2025 All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\", \"score\": 0.9999902857210866, \"rank\": 7.603133338578162e-06, \"text\": \"TV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\"}, {\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6988246592918856e-18, \"text\": \"Sakshi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc